        "rich_text_DjXatq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>More than gemstones, diamonds symbolize dreams, hope, and achievement. Diamond-buyers today want more than stunning designs; they seek beauty with values, and Lab Grown Diamonds fit the bill. But what is a Lab Grown Diamond? Are they real? Do they shine like natural ones?</p><p>Lab Grown Diamonds are 100% real, offering the same sparkle and brilliance as mined ones. Made in labs, they are special as they come without the environmental cost or ethical concerns.  In this blog, we’ll explore everything you need to know about Lab Grown Diamonds, decoding HPHT or what the CVD diamond process is, the myths surrounding them, and why they’re emerging as a popular choice.</p>",
